<h2>Walk Your Way to 15K and WIN an Inghams Walking Holiday</h2>
<p>National Walking Month is here! Lace up those boots and join the #YouSetThePace challenge for a chance to <strong>WIN an incredible 7 night Inghams Walking Holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Austria</a> for two</strong>. *<a href="#terms" data-anchor="#terms">T&amp;Cs Apply</a></p>
<h3>The Challenge</h3>
<p>This challenge is for everyone! Whether you prefer leisurely strolls, invigorating hikes, or long-distance treks, you set your own pace over the course of 4 weeks and walk your way to 15k.</p>
<p>Mark your calendars! The challenge starts <strong>Friday 10th May</strong> and ends <strong>Thursday 6th June 2024.</strong></p>
<h4>Join Our Strava Club to WIN</h4>
<p>To be in with a chance of winning, you need to join and complete our You Set The Pace 15km walking challenge on Strava.</p>
<p>If you haven’t already, you’ll need to download Strava, and join our club. It’s free, easy to use, and connects you with a fantastic supportive community to celebrate all your outdoor walks and hikes.</p>
<p> </p>
