<h2 style="text-align: center;">Join Our Strava Club</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Ready to put your steps to the test? Join the challenge today and you could be trekking the stunning Alpine landscapes of Austria this summer. Boots on. Get set. Go!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/70b350895a5d4ceeaa62215a223e24b5" href="https://www.strava.com/clubs/Inghams" target="_blank" title="Strava Challenge Inghams" class="c-btn">Join Challenge</a></p>
